
Carolina has lived next to Harry Styles ever since she moved to the small town. They have hated each other, especially since they have blackmailed each other numerous times.
But something changes.
And that something is their bodies.
Now Carolina is Harry and Harry is Carolina or is Carolina, Carolina but also Harry and Harry is Carolina but is Harry?
Doesn't matter. Anyway, they find out much about each other and they might gain feelings also. But can they get out of each other's bodies first?
